es/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋條片中間咪又係俾d差佬搜左身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n行為不檢</blockquote><br />\n無行為不檢 佢而家無露賓周"},{"pid":"c11c9108adb8a0c05dbd10baea519012eeb88250","tid":146584,"uid":9794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T09:27:05.000Z","msg":"睇錯搜隻金毛身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f9ba2c4784a7b576d4b7637048bdd205bba557","tid":146584,"uid":10157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T09:32:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>下咁都叫玩返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 剩係見到一個金毛係到發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁點解唔拘捕金毛 ?</blockquote><br />\n發癲都要拘捕佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋條片中間咪又係俾d差佬搜左身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n行為不檢</blockquote><br />\n無行為不檢 佢而家無露賓周</blockquote><br />\n佢要拉你露唔露都屈到你<br />\n擺明比條金毛兇到驚發癲比佢打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76b38efb5f844c4e700125dcc68dbff9f1e49a24","tid":146584,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T09:43:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4cdb4f58244514f6c1f3df92533efa3d6927a79","tid":146584,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T09:44:58.000Z","msg":"在法律上，警方有權在任何時間對任何可疑人士搜身，但必須要有充份理由，所以，在你被搜身之前，你必須確定下列數點： <br />\n<br />\n1. 你是否被拘捕； <br />\n2. 你必須問清楚警方搜身的目的及所找尋的可疑物品； <br />\n3. 最好有旁人做證，目擊搜身的細節； <br />\n4. 你可以要求到警署才接受搜身，最好帶有證人。 <br />\n<br />\n要清楚你是自願到警署搜身的，如果你沒有被拘捕，你應該有權在搜身後自由離去。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.answers.yahoo.com/question/index?qid=20080304000051KK00017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.answers.yahoo.com%2Fquestion%2Findex%3Fqid%3D20080304000051KK00017&d=3XxoN59xZ6GKXDea4epuEwhMEkA7P3Wv%2